metadata.name: Loneliness
metadata.description:
Sometimes in our life we want to be alone. In fact, this loneliness is like a medicine. Spending time with animals, going out in nature, being away from people. to recognize the creatures we share the world we live in. This story tells you the emotions I felt. Men and women, it doesn't matter. Loneliness has no gender.
